tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE performance_reports (
    report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_id UUID,
    report_date DATE,
    metrics JSONB,
    outcomes JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (
    supplier_id INT,
    year INT,
    month INT,
    revenue DECIMAL(10, 2),
    orders_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE order_details (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    supplier_id INT,
    order_date DATE,
    delivery_date DATE,
    order_status VARCHAR(50)
);
